Additional Terms for WiFi Hotspot Billing Systems:

This software is designed for legitimate WiFi hotspot billing systems and 
payment processing. Use of this software for illegal activities, fraud, or 
unauthorized access to networks is strictly prohibited.

The software integrates with IOTEC payment gateway and requires proper 
authentication and authorization. Users must comply with all applicable 
laws and regulations regarding payment processing and telecommunications.

Database connections and payment processing should be conducted in 
accordance with data protection regulations and best security practices. 